---
alwaysApply: true
---

This project is a Next.js frontend for a professional portfolio.

Deployment:
- AWS Amplify (connected to GitLab) is the deployment platform for the frontend.
- Always prioritize AWS Amplify-compatible configurations (build output, caching, environment variables, rewrites/redirects, image optimization, and runtime settings).

Backend:
- Java Spring Boot API hosted on AWS ECS at https://api.caseycapozzi.com.
- Prefer calling the API via the `api.caseycapozzi.com` origin (not the website root domain).

Infrastructure:
- Custom domain `caseycapozzi.com` managed via AWS Route 53.
- Assume production traffic reaches Amplify (frontend) and ECS (API) behind their respective AWS-managed endpoints.

